Andres Iniesta made his Barcelona debut against Manchester United in the 2002-03 season . 
  Louis van Gaal gave Iniesta his first team debut during his time at the Nou Camp . 
  Iniesta says he is grateful to Van Gaal for giving him the chance . 
  The Spain international also says his Champions League final goal against Chelsea in 2009 was the most important day of his career . 
 